{"tid":845482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔撚係掛] 宇宙G.E.M.殺入Marvel做超級英雄","createTime":"2018-10-02T16:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T15:08:10.000Z","uid":14788,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"159380f27c7425cf72190ace9ed3d4eb3c23808d","tid":845482,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"上年年尾歌手宇宙G.E.M.（鄧紫棋）就喺社交網甫咗張，同被喻為「漫威之父」嘅美國漫畫家史丹利（Stan Lee）合照，唔少網民都估佢哋會唔會有合作？答案仲於揭曉啦，G.E.M.成為Marvel其中一個超級英雄，真係恭喜晒！ <br />\n<br />\n話說啱啱喺上海舉行嘅「斯坦．李動漫宇宙展（Stan Lee's Comic Universe）」活動，年屆95歲嘅Stan Lee就冇出席，作為特別嘉賓嘅G.E.M.除咗晒唱功之外仲有個特別任務，就係宣布以佢作藍本嘅超級英雄終於面世，個名就叫做「JEWEL」，呢名同G.E.M.係相呼應都可以解作珠寶，好有心思喎！不過雖然話照住佢整，除咗對眼同埋着住G.E.M.最愛嘅緊身褲之外，其他地方就唔多覺有幾相似，唔知係咪配合番佢歌手嘅身份，JEWEL手執兩支類似演唱會歌迷用嘅應援棒做武器，而其他能力就暫時未有公布。"},{"pid":"be6a1868be29039da859fa26065958e7594f859d","tid":845482,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野品味"},{"pid":"f4ab4a0c6554d92353e20ebbb778e08673e52b42","tid":845482,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"以佢作藍本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35479a762b41b3dfec680506814e09036119bae","tid":845482,"uid":27188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"皮褲女俠"},{"pid":"5378789f0730f95cb5b577d511ede1ec72acdd02","tid":845482,"uid":156217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"能力：兒夜姨野以夜儀野"},{"pid":"006a1eb78cbef6344c29fcadcd66f00493cc1e0a","tid":845482,"uid":106230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"能力咪鳩叫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1943dd03ae1562be66211295a8532369f3476288","tid":845482,"uid":127292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{